Don't trust me alone with you.

624
00:37:08.885 --> 00:37:10.388
How's the hand?

625
00:37:11.958 --> 00:37:13.660
Have you slept?

626
00:37:14.367 --> 00:37:16.347
You look tired.

627
00:37:16.501 --> 00:37:18.967
It's important you
take care of yourself.

628
00:37:19.162 --> 00:37:21.033
preserve you strength.

629
00:37:21.221 --> 00:37:23.168
I've made a few requests.

630
00:37:23.276 --> 00:37:26.272
nothing scandalous.
just a couple of books.

631
00:37:26.371 --> 00:37:27.909
Claire almost died tonight.

632
00:37:28.028 --> 00:37:30.649
I like to read before bed.

633
00:37:31.071 --> 00:37:33.655
Calms the mind. helps me sleep.

634
00:37:33.762 --> 00:37:35.489
She almost died.

635
00:37:35.684 --> 00:37:37.452
the woman you profess to love.

636
00:37:37.577 --> 00:37:39.777
Yeah. but she didn't.

637
00:37:39.880 --> 00:37:41.845
I was hoping you'd save her.

638
00:37:42.119 --> 00:37:44.074
An heroic victory by the leading man

639
